            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nerone Claudio Caesare <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> Germanico <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Antistio Vetere co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendis</ex></expan> Augustis <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Iulius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Qui</abbr><ex>rina</ex></expan> Secundus legatus pro <lb n="5"/>praetore hospitium fecit cum <lb n="6"/>decurionibus et colonis colonia <lb n="7"/>Iulia <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usta</ex></expan> legionis VII Tupusuctu sibi <lb n="8"/>liberis posterisque suis eosque pa<lb break="no" n="9"/>trocinio suo tuendos recepit <lb n="10"/>agentibus legatis <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Caecilio <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Palatina Firmano <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Pomponio <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Vindice
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hospitium-Vertrag.</p>
            </div>
